<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Failed</title>
    <style>
        .bodydy {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 150px;
        }
        .failContainer {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin-top: 150px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #dc3545;
        }
        p {
            color: #333333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007bff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<div class="bodydy">
    <div class="failContainer">
        <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
        <p>Unfortunately, your payment could not be processed at this time.</p>
        <p>Please <a href="/user/myOrderPage/{{id}}">click here</a> to return to the your order page and try again.</p>
        <button type="button" class="btn bg-cart" style="background-color: #C7B0E2; ">
                    <a href="/user" style="text-decoration: none;"><i class="fa fa-cart-plus mr-2"></i> Continue Shopping</a>
                </button>    
    </div>
</div>
</html>
